{"article_id":"Ck7RihrVWVVn47d5","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Fired FBI director James Comey will testify openly to the Senate Intelligence Committee","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"that he believed","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"President Donald Trump was specifically attempting to influence him into ending the investigation of former national security adviser Michael Flynn 's possible ties to Russia .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"Comey 's testimony is not until tomorrow ,","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"but the advance written version of his prepared statements is now available through the Senate Intelligence Committee 's site .","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"And what it shows affirms what has been leaked through sources to the media for several weeks :","depth":3},{"id":6,"text":"Comey believed","depth":4},{"id":7,"text":"that Trump was unduly attempting to influence an investigation ,","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"that he wanted Comey 's `` loyalty , ''","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"and that he wanted Comey to somehow clear the Russia discussion off the table .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"The full seven-page document may be read here .","depth":3},{"id":11,"text":"But below are some pivotal highlights .","depth":3},{"id":12,"text":"Comey establishes early on","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"that did n't ever feel compelled to document private conversations with President Barack Obama","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"because there were only ever two :","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"I felt compelled to document my first conversation with the President-Elect in a memo .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"To ensure accuracy ,","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"I began to type it on a laptop in an FBI vehicle outside Trump Tower the moment","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"I walked out of the meeting .","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"Creating written records immediately after one-on-one conversations with Mr. Trump was my practice from that point forward .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"This had not been my practice in the past .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"I spoke alone with President Obama twice in person","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"( and never on the phone ) -","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"once in 2015","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"to discuss law enforcement policy issues","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"and a second time , briefly ,","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"for him to say goodbye in late 2016 .","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"In neither of those circumstances did I memorialize the discussions .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"I can recall nine one-on-one conversations with President Trump in four months-three in person and six on the phone .","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"Trump and Comey 's first one-on-one meeting was at a dinner in the Green Room in the White House .","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"Here is where","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"Comey claims","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"that Trump demanded Comey 's loyalty .","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"The president did n't seem to grasp","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"that the FBI is supposed to maintain a level of independence from the White House :","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"I added","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"that I was not `` reliable '' in the way","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"politicians use that word ,","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"but he could always count on me to tell him the truth .","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"I added","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"that I was not on anybody 's side politically","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"and could not be counted on in the traditional political sense ,","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"a stance","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"I said","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"was in his best interest as the President .","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"A few moments later , the President said ,","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"`` I need loyalty ,","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"I expect loyalty . ''","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"I did n't move ,","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"speak , or change my facial expression in any way during the awkward silence","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"that followed .","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"We simply looked at each other in silence .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"The conversation then moved on ,","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"but he returned to the subject near the end of our dinner .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"Again Trump said","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"he wanted loyalty .","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"Comey responded","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"that he would offer honesty .","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"Trump apparently decided to combine the words","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"and say","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"that he wanted `` honest loyalty . ''","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"Comey let that sit","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"without correcting further .","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"Trump also asked Comey to consider investigating the whole `` Russian hookers '' story","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"to prove","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"it did n't happen .","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"Comey pointed out","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"that the result would be creating a narrative","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"that the FBI was investigating Trump personally ,","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"which was something","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"Trump was trying to avoid .","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"In February , Trump took Comey aside","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"to ask him to try to get the Flynn investigation dropped :","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"The President then returned to the topic of Mike Flynn ,","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"saying ,","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"`` He is a good guy","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"and has been through a lot . ''","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"He repeated","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"that Flynn had n't done anything wrong on his calls with the Russians ,","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"but had misled the Vice President .","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"He then said ,","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"`` I hope","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"you can see your way clear","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"to letting this go ,","depth":14},{"id":84,"text":"to letting Flynn go .","depth":14},{"id":85,"text":"He is a good guy .","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"I hope","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"you can let this go . ''","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"I replied only","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"that `` he is a good guy . ''","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"( In fact , I had a positive experience","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"dealing with Mike Flynn","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"when he was a colleague as Director of the Defense Intelligence Agency at the beginning of my term at FBI . )","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"I did not say","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"I would `` let this go . ''","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"Comey then prepared a memo","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"that explained wto the FBI leadership what had happened :","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"I had understood the President to be requesting","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"that we drop any investigation of Flynn in connection with false statements about his conversations with the Russian ambassador in December .","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"They decided not to tell the investigative team and the Department of Justice lawyers","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"working with them","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"about the president 's request ,","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"concerned","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"that it might `` infect '' the investigation .","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"Comey did","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"( as was reported yesterday evening )","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"ask Attorney General Jeff Sessions to prevent the president from attempting to communicate directly with him .","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"Comey says","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"Sessions did n't respond .","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"He did not tell Sessions about Trump 's request","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"to drop the investigation .","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"In March , Trump called Comey","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"and makes it clear","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"he was very agitated","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"that all the discussion about Russia 's influence wo n't go away :","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"He said","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"he had nothing to do with Russia ,","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"had not been involved with hookers in Russia ,","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"and had always assumed","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"he was being recorded","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"when in Russia .","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"He asked what we could do","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"to `` lift the cloud .","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"'' I responded","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"that we were investigating the matter as quickly","depth":14},{"id":125,"text":"as we could ,","depth":14},{"id":126,"text":"and that there would be great benefit ,","depth":15},{"id":127,"text":"if we did n't find anything ,","depth":15},{"id":128,"text":"to our having done the work well .","depth":14},{"id":129,"text":"He agreed ,","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"but then re-emphasized the problems","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"this was causing him .","depth":13},{"id":132,"text":"He wanted Comey to `` get that fact out ''","depth":13},{"id":133,"text":"that Trump himself was not under investigation .","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"( That 's a recurring theme in Comey 's testimony . )","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"Comey did , in fact , tell Trump multiple times","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"that he was not personally under investigation .","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"Trump definitely remembered that detail","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"when he ultimately fired Comey .","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"But Comey also notes","depth":9},{"id":140,"text":"that the Justice Department did n't want to make public statements to that effect in the event","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"that circumstances changed","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"and they did have to investigate Trump ,","depth":11},{"id":143,"text":"because then they 'd have to make another public statement .","depth":11},{"id":144,"text":"And then there 's their final phone call ,","depth":8},{"id":145,"text":"dated April 11","depth":9},{"id":146,"text":"( Comey was fired on May 9 ) :","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"On the morning of April 11 , the President called me","depth":13},{"id":148,"text":"and asked","depth":14},{"id":149,"text":"what I had done about his request","depth":15},{"id":150,"text":"that I `` get out ''","depth":16},{"id":151,"text":"that he is not personally under investigation .","depth":16},{"id":152,"text":"I replied","depth":14},{"id":153,"text":"that I had passed his request to the Acting Deputy Attorney General ,","depth":14},{"id":154,"text":"but I had not heard back .","depth":13},{"id":155,"text":"He replied","depth":13},{"id":156,"text":"that `` the cloud '' was getting in the way of his ability","depth":14},{"id":157,"text":"to do his job .","depth":14},{"id":158,"text":"He said","depth":13},{"id":159,"text":"that perhaps he would have his people reach out to the Acting Deputy Attorney General .","depth":13},{"id":160,"text":"I said","depth":13},{"id":161,"text":"that was the way","depth":14},{"id":162,"text":"his request should be handled .","depth":14},{"id":163,"text":"I said","depth":13},{"id":164,"text":"the White House Counsel should contact the leadership of DOJ","depth":14},{"id":165,"text":"to make the request ,","depth":15},{"id":166,"text":"which was the traditional channel .","depth":15},{"id":167,"text":"He said","depth":13},{"id":168,"text":"he would do that","depth":13},{"id":169,"text":"and added ,","depth":13},{"id":170,"text":"`` Because I have been very loyal to you , very loyal ;","depth":14},{"id":171,"text":"we had that thing","depth":15},{"id":172,"text":"you know . ''","depth":15},{"id":173,"text":"I did not reply or ask him what he meant by `` that thing . ''","depth":10},{"id":174,"text":"I said only","depth":12},{"id":175,"text":"that the way","depth":14},{"id":176,"text":"to handle it","depth":14},{"id":177,"text":"was to have the White House Counsel call the Acting Deputy Attorney General .","depth":13},{"id":178,"text":"He said","depth":13},{"id":179,"text":"that was what he would do","depth":13},{"id":180,"text":"and the call ended .","depth":12},{"id":181,"text":"That was the last time","depth":9},{"id":182,"text":"I spoke with President Trump .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":365,"left":192,"right":364,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":192,"left":187,"right":191,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":187,"left":185,"right":186,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":185,"left":0,"right":184,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":184,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":186,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":191,"left":5,"right":190,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":190,"left":6,"right":189,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":189,"left":7,"right":188,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":188,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":364,"left":193,"right":363,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":193,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":363,"left":251,"right":362,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":251,"left":209,"right":250,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":209,"left":195,"right":208,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":195,"left":12,"right":194,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":194,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":208,"left":199,"right":207,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":199,"left":198,"right":19,"relation":"elabor